I think you want to make Sub Main run ENTIRE function, and DON'T EXIT as sub main is executed.  
I have written answer of your question here : http://stackoverflow.com/questions/8168304/vb-net-program-with-no-ui/17907335#17907335

    Sub Main()
        'Write whatever you want, and add this code at the END:
        Application.Run
    End Sub
